definition.de:
Eine Liste von ergänzenden Sammlungen, die von Interesse sein könnten.
siehe [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property)
definition.en:
A list of supplementary Collections which may be of interest.
see [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property)
definition.fr:
Une liste de collections supplémentaires qui peuvent être d'intérêt.
voir [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property)
definition.es:
Una lista de Colecciones complementarias que pueden ser de interés.
ver [https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property](https://www.w3.org/TR/activitypub/#streams-property)
